                      and mirin. Mix thoroughly until it forms a smooth paste.
                      Set aside.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li
                  class="text-balance text-lg font-semibold text-dark 2xl:text-xl dark:text-stone-200"
                >
                  Prepare the Soup
                  <ul
                    role="list"
                    class="dark:marker-primary mt-1 list-disc space-y-2 text-pretty ps-5 font-normal text-stone-600 marker:text-secondary 2xl:text-lg dark:text-stone-400"
