                      seasonings to taste. Keep the soup warm on low heat.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li
                  class="text-balance text-lg font-semibold text-dark 2xl:text-xl dark:text-stone-200"
                >
                  Cook the Ramen Noodles
                  <ul
                    role="list"
                    class="dark:marker-primary mt-1 list-disc space-y-2 text-pretty ps-5 font-normal text-stone-600 marker:text-secondary 2xl:text-lg dark:text-stone-400"
                  >
                    <li>
                      In a separate pot, bring water to a boil. Cook the ramen
                      noodles according to the package instructions, usually
                      for 2-3 minutes, or until al dente.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      Once cooked, drain the noodles and rinse them quickly
                      under cold water to stop the cooking process. Set aside.
                    </li>
